reviewText: My 18 month old and my 3.5 year old really love this DVD, and the songs are really catchy! I kind of like watching it myself :)
Both my sons love it & enjoy singing to the songs. Great purchase.
A great dvd that my 3 daughters can't get enough of. I hope there will be more made.
Excellent product. Exactly what I need.

I can't say enough good words about the Super Simple Songs DVD collections. I got this one for my 1 yr old, but my 7 and 9 watch it with the same pleasure. They never get bored of it, my baby applauds at it and we still play it, even though Halloween is over. We can't wait for the new collections to be out!
Perfect dvd for little children and even for the parents!
Grandkids and classroom kids/preschool loved it.
My son favorite! Wish it was a little longer though!
Great songs for preschool and elementary level children.
My grandkids just love these Super Simple Song DVDs.  Great buy.
My 3 year old loves the songs!
